parameters:
Bunny-chan: Um, about the conditions for the revenge
match... "Naked public defecation" is what we agreed on...
Are you really going to do it...? Honestly, I don't want to
witness it...

Memimi: Don't be stubborn, Anomalocaris Mosman!! Public
defecation is really the end! I set a condition that I
thought was absolutely impossible too!?

Anomalocaris Mosman: Idiot... Don't underestimate me!! I can
do something as simple as defecating naked anytime!! Just
watch... you shit!!!

The villain Anomalocaris Mosman... He too was a man who was
once the boss of an organization with many members.
Following behind a young girl like Memimi was unbearable for
his pride. Just as she had fought without shame, he too is
willing to sacrifice himself to make a comeback...
Anomalocaris Mosman: Being naked is nothing... Uoooo...!!

Memimi: Ugh... This is, on the contrary, more like a
punishment game for us who have to watch... Did I make a
mistake in setting the conditions...

Anomalocaris Mosman: Gah... To think that the time would
come for me to strip off my villain suit in front of
people...
